text: Ranikhet District is newly proposed district to split Almora district in the state of Uttarakhand, India. Its area is 1397 km2 and population is 322,408 ==Tehsils== *Ranikhet *Salt *Bhikiyasain *Dwarahat *Chaukhutia *Syalde ==Blocks== *Eight ==Visiting places== Ranikhet is a hill station. ==Religious places== Jhula Devi Temple, Ranikhet *Jhula Devi Temple ==References== Category:Proposed districts of Uttarakhand
